stories.text:
Hey HN Community, saw this exciting announcement from the team at Disco, an all in one platform for live learning experiences, that I thought was relevant to many of you in the group.

They just launched a new 4-week accelerator to help an exclusive group of top thought leaders/experts/creators convert their IP into a premium live learning experience. They're teaming up with some incredible instructors including @BillyBroas (who has worked with Tiago Forte + David Perrell) and Suzzanne Howard (IDEO U founder) to help you make it happen!

The deadline for applications is September 1st, so definitely recommend applying! Creators like Adam Davidson (https://www.disco.co/accelerator) are participating.
